latestPosts.caption:
As we step into 2025, it’s impossible not to look back at the year that was—2024, the year of horror-comedies and sequels. Films like ‘Stree 2’ delivered everything from jump scares and one-liners to chart-topping dance numbers, smashing records to become the year’s highest grosser. Among its ensemble cast, Shraddha Kapoor stole the spotlight, living up to her IG bio as she dominated both the box office and social media.

Kicking off the year with our twin issue, we’re equipping you with all the essentials for 2025—from the biggest fashion and micro beauty trends to a style horoscope to craft the perfect wardrobe. Additionally, we’re bringing you the names across music, film, sports, art, and the digital space that are set to own the year ahead. Here’s to ringing in the new year with fresh styles and perspectives.

Shraddha is wearing a funnel-neck jumper, appliqué leggings, both @hermes; ankle boots, @jimmychoo; textured rings, both @palmonas_official
